title: Rise & Grind (w/ Shane Gillis & Justin Silver)
description: Dan & Jay check out the morning schedule for Mark Wahlberg and it just doesn't seem right. Justin Silver & Shane Gillis join the show and Shane recaps his performance at the Bonfire Live Holiday Show the night before.
